Package: synopR
Title: Tidy Decoding of SYNOP Meteorological Messages
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Ezequiel", "Elias", , "elezeru15@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Decode raw SYNOP messages into tidy data frames. Supports batch 
    processing of messages from the same station, extracting data from 
    Sections 0, 1, and 3, including temperature, pressure, wind, clouds, and precipitation.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
